title: Hour 1 - Jeanie Buss Gets Cryptic
itunes:title: Hour 1 - Jeanie Buss Gets Cryptic
description:
Jason Smith and Mike Harmon are in for Dan Patrick and the Danettes on this very special 4th of July. Jeanie Buss sends out a very cryptic tweet at midnight and the guys try and dissect every portion of it. Kevin Durant’s Nets drama continues on this holiday, and why not? Jason and Mike discuss all the tweets, rumors and everything in between. Plus, NFL Insider and host of the Pull Up Pod with CJ McCollum Jordan Schultz joins the guys to discuss everything NFL and NBA!

 

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
